00:00:05.269 --> 00:00:07.842
Hi and welcome back to my kitchen

00:00:08.111 --> 00:00:12.731
Today ,I will make a yogurt lamb stew

00:00:13.039 --> 00:00:15.237
the ingredients are very simple:

00:00:15.443 --> 00:00:25.008
1 pound(450 grams) boneless lamb meat,cut into 1 inch cubes

00:00:25.301 --> 00:00:36.438
1 cup cooked(canned) chickpeas

00:00:37.654 --> 00:00:43.698
1 medium onion(thinly sliced)

00:00:44.709 --> 00:00:51.605
750 grams full fat yogurt

00:00:51.605 --> 00:00:57.685
I prefer Balkan style yogurt

00:00:58.189 --> 00:00:59.839
1/8 teaspoon  ground white pepper

00:01:00.137 --> 00:01:01.772
1/8 teaspoon  ground black pepper

00:01:02.105 --> 00:01:04.050
1/8 teaspoon ground all spice

00:01:04.395 --> 00:01:05.844
salt to taste

00:01:06.194 --> 00:01:09.359
1/2 cup chicken broth

00:01:09.732 --> 00:01:13.130
1 tablespoon corn starch

00:01:13.707 --> 00:01:16.219
3 cardamom pods

00:01:17.314 --> 00:02:06.457
First, mix the ground spices with 1/8 teaspoon of salt and rub the meat well

00:02:17.885 --> 00:02:29.179
heat 2 tablespoons of corn oil in a medium sized pot

00:02:29.647 --> 00:02:51.489
over medium-high heat sear the meat on all sides until lightly browned

00:02:56.997 --> 00:03:22.972
Add the onion and the cardamom

00:03:45.408 --> 00:03:50.866
saute for 5 minutes

00:03:58.918 --> 00:04:06.823
add 3 cups pf boiling water

00:04:07.179 --> 00:04:13.359
bring to a boil

00:04:15.714 --> 00:04:38.442
skim the impurities

00:04:40.018 --> 00:04:57.323
Cover the pot and simmer until the meat is fork tender(about 90 minutes)

00:05:10.709 --> 00:05:12.981
Cook the yogurt

00:05:13.262 --> 00:05:40.127
Off the heat,blend the yogurt with the chicken stock and the corn starch until foamy

00:05:40.127 --> 00:06:19.598
Cook the yogurt using medium to high heat until it boils stirring constantly

00:06:20.390 --> 00:06:37.424
Add the  boiling yogurt and chickpeas to the cooked meat

00:06:37.424 --> 00:06:42.354
Adjust the salt and cook for 5-10 minutes

00:06:42.572 --> 00:06:46.677
Serve hot with white cooked rice

00:06:46.928 --> 00:06:50.060
Sahteen

00:06:50.312 --> 00:06:52.385
Sahteen

